Hi <%= @user.name || 'there' %>,

We received a request to reset the password for your <%= @operator.name %> account associated with this email address.

To choose a new password, please click the link below or paste it into your browser:

<% if @reset_token.present? %><%= edit_password_reset_url(@reset_token, email: @user.email, subdomain: @operator.subdomain) %><% else %>There was an issue generating your password reset link. Please try requesting a new password reset.<% end %>

This link will expire in two hours for your security.

If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email and your password will remain unchanged.

If you have any questions or need further assistance, please contact our support team.

Thank you
